[0.016, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J"]
[0.001, "o", "    Graphenium: Provenance-aware structural memory for AI agents\r\n\r\n    Most code tools help humans search files.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Graphenium gives AI agents a durable, queryable map of your repo.\r\n"]
[3.009, "o", "\r\n    It replaces grep-and-trace navigation, not source-code understanding.\r\n"]
[2.011, "o", "\r\n    $ gm run . --no-semantic --no-viz\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Graph: 957 nodes | 1941 edges | 22 communities | schema 0.2.0\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    AST-only, no API key needed. Runs in under 2 seconds.\r\n"]
[2.007, "o", "\r\n    $ gm query \"what depends on the serve module\" --budget 400\r\n\r\n"]
[0.029, "o", "# Graph Query: serve module handlers mcp\r\n\r\nFound 53 relevant nodes (of 957)\r\n\r\nAST-only tuning active: suppressing common import/generated-code noise by default\r\n\r\nFilter: generated/template/vendor paths excluded\r\n\r\nFound 53 node(s)\r\n\r\n## handlers (code [community 3])\r\nFile: ~/Documents/Code/Graphenium/src/serve/handlers.rs\r\nSpan: L1:C1-L2547:C1\r\nMatch: direct keyword match on label, id, path for `handlers`, `serve` (score 2.00)\r\n\r\nConnections:\r\n- handlers `contains` reload_graph_reports_parse_error [tree-sitter:resolved]\r\n- handlers `contains` summarize_file_group_by_community [tree-sitter:resolved]\r\n- handlers `contains` summarize_file_no_match_returns_clean_message [tree-sitter:resolved]\r\n- handlers `contains` summarize_file_handles_backslash_paths [tree-sitter:resolved]\r\n- handlers `contains` summarize_file_lists_symbols_matching_suffix [tree-sitter:resolved]\r\n- handlers `contains` reload_graph_missing_path_without_default [tree-sitter:resolved]\r\n- handlers `contains` reload_graph_swaps_state [tree-sitte"]
